data.title: Niagara's Jack Gatecliff Arena special to NHL star Alex Pietrangelo
data.meta_description: Written By Brandon Caputo of the Armchair GM’s Sports Network Alex Pietrangelo is now a two-time Stanley Cup champion in his 15th National Hockey League (NHL) season but the now 34-year old King City, Ontario native still looks back fondly of his two years spent in the Niagara Region, playing at the old Jack Gatecliff Arena dawning…
